name:
Photon 1.15 
(c) 2021 ermouth 

Run attachment `index.html` to start Photon. 

See https://github.com/ermouth/couch-photon 
repo for more details.
versions:
## 1.15.20

Doc editor received `Clone...` button, which allows to save the doc
under new \_id into another DB bucket.

Fixed issues with creating/opening docs having `/` in \_id; also 
added fallback `_all_docs?key=` read if normal doc GET returns 404, 
which might happen with misconfigured proxies.

## 1.15.16

Added HEX representation for text fields in grid views, minor fixes.
Added Patreon sponsor link to GitHub.

## 1.15.15

Grid view columns now support type casting postfixes which convert
cell value into more readable format, like `.doc.stamp /dt` converts
numerical timestamps into date-time. Available cast functions reveal
themselves in autocomplete drop-down on typing ` /`.

## 1.15.12

Copying grid view data to GoogleDocs Table no more copies internal 
Photon navigation links.

Minor UI fixes and improvements.

## 1.15.11

Added `../` button for views, it opens view’s DB doc list in a
separate tab.

Value cells of grid view now open row JSON on click.

## 1.15.9

Minor UI tweaks: added `Close all` button at the bottom of 
left panel; timestamp-like numbers has a tooltip with date;
wheel-click on a tab closes it, etc.

## 1.15.8

Minor result panels redesign: less borders, more air. Sync 
tasks done now have individual `Restart` buttons at right 
of task rows.

Grid result view now highlights cells that match search input.

## 1.15.5

Minor left panel improvements, design now is more coherent and 
sleek. Click on deleted doc in `_changes` feed opens deleted 
doc correctly.

## 1.15.2

Added left panel / top bar switch to match wide monitors better. 
Vertical panel only available for 1420px+ wide screens.

List performance is significantly improved, DB list is ok for 
nodes with up to ~2…3k buckets.

## 1.14

Added grid (table) representation mode for docs lists, view and 
Mango queries. Tables are copy/pastable to Excel. 

Added Include docs option for `/_all_docs` view, it is turned on 
automatically for grid view mode.

Views now memoize their particular source code editor state, as 
well as reduce level and grid settings.

## 1.12

Added ZIP dump/restore. A [Delete DB] dlg now offers to re-create 
DB(s) after deletion. Several JSON editor fixes and improvements. 
Task list grouping improved. 

TT Mono font excluded from the Photon package. 

## 1.11

Added `/_changes` feed view, added compound index stats for 
ddocs view.

## 1.10

Added index stats for each ddoc in ddocs view; also a lot of 
slight UI improvements.

## 1.9

Added: group DB sync; Couch perf test; CouchDB v3 support. 

## 1.8

Improved JSON editor, added `/_stats` graphs.

## 1.7

Added structured diff for doc revisions.

## 1.6

New features: editor for text-based attachments and doc purge. 
DB view received `db/_design_docs` and `db/_local_docs` modes.

## 1.4

Added access restrictions, Photon no more starts without 
authorization.

## 1.2

Added in-place editors for Erlang, JS and Mango view syntax.

## 0.9.99

More or less usable version with all basic features. March, 2018.
